    <div class="section-column">
        <div class="sticky">
        <div class="inner-column">
            <h1 class="pixel-font uppercase">FAQ</h1>
            <div class="spacer-large"></div>

            <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">Do you accept Bitcoin payments?</h4>
            <p class="text-large">Yes — Bitcoin and Lightning payments are accepted at checkout. Other payment options include credit card and iDEAL.</p>

            <div class="spacer"></div>

            <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">Where are your products made?</h4>
            <p class="text-large">Almost everything is produced locally in the Netherlands, working with preferred suppliers I trust. The only exception is sticker packs, which are printed elsewhere.</p>

            <div class="spacer"></div>

            <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">When will my order ship?</h4>
            <p class="text-large">Orders are shipped once a week from the studio in Amsterdam. You'll receive a track & trace code by email so you can follow your package along the way.</p>

            <div class="spacer"></div>

            <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">How do digital orders work?</h4>
            <p class="text-large">Digital products are delivered instantly. After completing your order you'll see the download link on the order summary page. You will also receive the link by email.</p>

            <div class="spacer"></div>

            <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">Can I return my order?</h4>
            <p class="text-large">I don't accept returns on limited runs. If your order arrives badly damaged, reach out and I'll make it right.</p>

            <div class="spacer"></div>

            <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">How do you use my data?</h4>
            <p class="text-large">Only to fulfil your order. Snipcart stores your order info and shipping address. Mollie handles payments. I use MyParcel to take care of shipping. Read the <a href="/terms/">Terms &amp; Conditions</a> and <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.</p>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
